      // Calculadora de Presi√≥n Arterial Media (PAM)
      function calcPAM() {
        const sbp = parseFloat(document.getElementById('pam-sbp').value);
        const dbp = parseFloat(document.getElementById('pam-dbp').value);
        const resultEl = document.getElementById('pam-result');
        if (isNaN(sbp) || isNaN(dbp)) {
          resultEl.textContent = 'Por favor, introduce n√∫meros v√°lidos.';
          return;
        }
        const map = (sbp + 2 * dbp) / 3;
        const classification = map >= 65 ? 'normal' : 'bajo';
        resultEl.textContent = `PAM: ${map.toFixed(1)} mmHg (valor ${classification}).`;
      }

      // Calculadora de √çndice de Masa Corporal (BMI)
      function calcBMI() {
        const weight = parseFloat(document.getElementById('bmi-weight').value);
        const height = parseFloat(document.getElementById('bmi-height').value);
        const resultEl = document.getElementById('bmi-result');
        if (isNaN(weight) || isNaN(height) || height <= 0) {
          resultEl.textContent = 'Por favor, introduce valores v√°lidos.';
          return;
        }
        const bmi = weight / (height * height);
        let category;
        if (bmi < 18.5) {
          category = 'bajo peso';
        } else if (bmi < 25) {
          category = 'peso saludable';
        } else if (bmi < 30) {
          category = 'sobrepeso';
        } else if (bmi < 35) {
          category = 'obesidad clase I';
        } else if (bmi < 40) {
          category = 'obesidad clase II';
        } else {
          category = 'obesidad clase III';
        }
        resultEl.textContent = `BMI: ${bmi.toFixed(1)} (${category}).`;
      }

      // Calculadora de tasa de goteo IV
      function calcDrip() {
        const volume = parseFloat(document.getElementById('drip-volume').value);
        const time = parseFloat(document.getElementById('drip-time').value);
        const factor = parseFloat(document.getElementById('drip-factor').value);
        const resultEl = document.getElementById('drip-result');
        if (isNaN(volume) || isNaN(time) || isNaN(factor) || time <= 0) {
          resultEl.textContent = 'Por favor, introduce valores v√°lidos.';
          return;
        }
        const rate = (volume * factor) / time;
        resultEl.textContent = `Tasa de goteo: ${rate.toFixed(1)} gotas/minuto.`;
      }
